 "blurb": "Holy Priest is TBC's raid-healing workhorse: Circle of Healing spam on melee stacks, Prayer of Mending bouncing on cooldown, Renew weaving between. Throughput is never the problem — mana is, and this gear list is built around spirit regen as much as raw +healing. This Phase 2 snapshot aggregates 273 top healing parses from Serpentshrine Cavern and Tempest Keep; the highest-consensus pick is Gloves of the Avatar at 84% usage.",
